title: Taco Beach
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small cafe serving Mexican cuisine. Vegan versions of tacos, nachos and burritos easily available. Extensive condiments and in-house-made hot sauces. American owner. Busy during peak periods so booking is recommended. Limited seating.
